<!-- Asteroid attibutes explained 
	distance: Minimum viewable distance observatory musthave to discover asteroid
	mass: Total blocks asteroid must have
	massVariability: (between 0 and 1) Randomness of the astroid size (size = mass  0.5 * mass * massVariability)
	richness: (between 0 and 1) ratio of ore to rock content, 1 = 100% ore
	richnessVariability: (between 0 and 1) Randomness of the richness
	probability: Probability relative to other asteroids of this asteroid showing up (probabilities are normalized between all asteroids)
	timeMultiplier: Multiplier on the time needed to mine the asteroid.
-->

<!-- ore attributes explained
	itemStack: unlocaillized name of a block or item optionally followed by a space and meta value (example "minecraft:coal 1" would be charcoal, coal metadata 1)
	chance: the chance of that ore being mined compared to other stacks in the astroid
-->

